WorkItem.Description: According to my Rawr v2.3.14 - Ymirjar's Lord's Gauntlets is less DPS (316.84) than Wrynn's Gauntlet of Conquest (371.16).  Am I missing something or is Rawr not calculating this correctly.  Ymirjar's numbers are all better across the board and its a higher level item.  Help me understand.  Thanks
WorkItem.Summary: Why would Ymirjar Lord's Gauntlets be less DPS than Wrynn's Gauntlet of Conquest

Comments.Message: It's probably your T9 2 or 4-piece set bonus that makes it better. Do you have any other pieces of T9 equipped?
I do have the legplates equipped.  Thank you for pointing out what I should of realized.  I'm an idiot.  I unequipped the Wrynn's legplates,  and Ymirjar did jump past Wrynn's in DPS.  Thank you.
